{"tid":2514491,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝人保安Stanley揭37年工作秘辛 追靈車護送張國榮最後一程盡情義","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T12:29:06.000Z","uid":82917,"like":111,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"53d16e1d51f3167fea74133b339e7d5f7d25802b","tid":2514491,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210503/YEJFEAZSJJCDHORB2P7MJB7RLA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR08TysRe3g5hwMpekdRCsje3BaBSIXI5zsTMYRo7mkbzxu1fdxr5ir0FOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210503%2FYEJFEAZSJJCDHORB2P7MJB7RLA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR08TysRe3g5hwMpekdRCsje3BaBSIXI5zsTMYRo7mkbzxu1fdxr5ir0FOY&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=bdbd23e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210503%2FYEJFEAZSJJCDHORB2P7MJB7RLA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR08TysRe3g5hwMpekdRCsje3BaBSIXI5zsTMYRo7mkbzxu1fdxr5ir0FOY&h=12c1c48d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210503/YEJFEAZSJJCDHORB2P7MJB7RLA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR08TysRe3g5hwMpekdRCsje3BaBSIXI5zsTMYRo7mkbzxu1fdxr5ir0FOY</a><br />\n<br />\n// Stanley曾為多位巨星提供服務，交情最深的是張國榮（哥哥），「好多謝哥哥，我入行只係20歲多啲，同而家比經驗差好遠，但哥哥冇嫌棄一個咁嘅𡃁仔，佢唔單止起用我、包容我，好多嘢係佢教我，譬如同佢出去食飯，餐桌禮儀佢會提點我，去到外地工作，英文講得唔太對，佢會指正我，我家庭上同佢傾偈，佢會畀到好好意見。有晚佢問我有冇諗過移民？當時啱啱97關係，佢話喺新加坡有朋友開公司，可以叫朋友聘請我去嗰邊做嘢搞移民，佢係會關心人去到咁嘅程度。」<br />\n<br />\n2003年4月1日哥哥離去那天，Stanley接到陳淑芬的電話趕到瑪麗醫院，「記得傍晚時分，陳太畀電話我，話哥哥出咗事，即刻過嚟瑪麗醫院，喺我開車過去嘅同時，好多傳媒行家甚至藝人都打畀我，問哥哥係咪出咗事，大家都知我同哥哥關係好好，因為礙於我嘅職業操守關係，只能扮到若無其事。」<br />\n<br />\n唐唐知道Stanley跟哥哥交情深，很信任他，不但將靈室的鎖匙給他保管，更讓他瞻仰哥哥遺容，「當時哥哥大殮，我喺殯儀館附近處理公仔，唐生專登搵人叫我，等埋我上嚟，哥哥先至入殮。」<br />\n<br />\n當哥哥出殯時，Stanley陪着靈車跑了一段路，親送哥哥最後一程，「好多人問過我點解有咁舉動，老實講我都唔知，只係諗住呢程係哥哥最後一程，再冇機會，我有需要喺隔鄰做一個保護。」儀式完成後，Stanley護送唐唐返加多利山，「返到屋企真係忍唔住，大家抱頭痛哭，可能嗰幾日太過集中做好件事，冇時間諗呢啲，反而完晒成件事，有咁嘅反應。」//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNMC8yw2XhLRBG9R5ERan9vUrsoxHD1s9DwGxNehYf6pi?filename=ZRS943O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRS943O.png&h=2a12dc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇字都想喊。。。miss u much <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b662faa5ebc2ea1f02fd859dcc781f8fbecef18","tid":2514491,"uid":310700,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"抽粉絲水嘅粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebabb2c9fdd5da5672a96fafa47b64e5973cb5da","tid":2514491,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b662faa5ebc2ea1f02fd859dcc781f8fbecef18","tid":2514491,"uid":310700,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"抽粉絲水嘅粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"即刻有衰嘢爆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b250cacc46ae919eb4e4528201a70b154ddab9e","tid":2514491,"uid":301749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0b662faa5ebc2ea1f02fd859dcc781f8fbecef18","tid":2514491,"uid":310700,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"抽粉絲水嘅粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"